_sText:
This map was inspired by a halo map I played at a friends house, although upon completing this map, I realised it look's nothing like the halo map I designed it to be like.

This map support's 12 t's and 12 ct's, there are vent's which can be used to access any part of the map along with 2 secret rooms.  There are 2 bombsites, one in the room across from the kitchen and one upstairs.  This map was originally going to be a deathmatch one, but I realized that although deathmatch is indeed possible, it has become too big to be w/out a bombsite.

PM me for any map requests you may have or for any mapping questions.

!!! THIS MAP INCLUDES A NAV FILE !!!
